  "content_body": "<div>\r\n\t<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/default/files/users/u5046/smoothie.jpg\" style=\"height:357px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<h2>Ingredients</h2>\r\n\r\n\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t<p>SERVINGS: MAKES ABOUT 2 CUPS</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>1&nbsp;banana, preferably frozen</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>2&nbsp;Medjool dates, pitted</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>&frac12;&nbsp;cup&nbsp;cold-brew coffee</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>&frac14;&nbsp;cup&nbsp;raw cashews, preferably soaked overnight</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>3&nbsp;tablespoons&nbsp;old-fashioned oats, preferably soaked overnight</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>1&nbsp;tablespoon&nbsp;unsweetened cocoa powder</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Pinch of ground cardamom</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Pinch of kosher salt</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\t</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\t<h2>Preparation</h2>\r\n\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Using smoothie or ice crush setting, pur\u00e9e banana, dates, coffee, cashews, oats, cocoa powder, cardamom, salt, and &frac12; cup ice in a blender until smooth.</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t<h2>NOTE: This power-breakfast smoothie will be extra smooth if you soak the nuts and oats in water overnight; drain before proceeding.</h2>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\r\n\t<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>",
